tegory:Living people]]\n[[Category:Women's association football forwards]]\n[[Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina women's footballers]]\n[[Category:Bosnia and Herzegovina women's international footballers]]\n\n\n{{BosniaHerzegovina-women-footy-bio-stub}}\n", "text_old": "{{Infobox football biography\n| name           = Marija Damjanovi\u0107\n| image          = \n| image_size     = \n| caption        =\n| fullname       = \n| birth_date     = {{Birth date and age|df=yes|2000|8|16}}<ref name=SW>{{Soccerway|id=464030|accessdate=15 April 2020}}</ref>\n| birth_place    = \n| height         = \n| position       = [[Forward (association football)|Forward]]<ref name=SW/>\n| currentclub    = [[FK Lokomotiva Br\u010dko|Lokomotiva]]\n| clubnumber     = \n| youthyears1    = \n| youthclubs1    = \n| collegeyears1  = \n| college1       = \n| collegecaps1   = | collegegoals1 = \n| years1         = \n| clubs1         = [[FK Lokomotiva Br\u010dko|Lokomotiva]]\n| caps1          = \n| goals1         = \n| nationalyears1 = 2016\u20132017\n| nationalteam1  = [[Bosnia and Herzegovina women's national under-17 football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina U17]]\n| nationalcaps1  = 6\n| nationalgoals1 = 0\n| nationalyears2 = 2017\u20132018\n| nationalteam2  = [[Bosnia and Herzegovina women's national under-19 football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina U19]]\n| nationalcaps2  = 6\n| nationalgoals2 = 1\n| nationalyears3 = 2019\u2013\n| nationalteam3  = [[Bosnia and Herzegovina women's national football team|Bosnia and Herzegovina]]\n| nationalcaps3  = 2\n| nationalgoals3 = 0\n| pcupdate = \n| ntupdate = 10 March 2020\n}}\n\n'''Marija Damjanovi\u0107''' (born 16 August 2000) is a Bosnia and Herzegovina [[women's association football|footballer]] who plays as a [[Forward (association football)|forward]] for [[Bosnia and Herzegovina Women's Premier League|\u017denska Premijer Liga BiH]] club [[FK Lokomotiva Br\u010dko|ZFK Lokomotiva Br\u010dko]] and the [[Bosnia and Herzegovina women's national football team|Bos