Fichte. Studi sul primato del pratico'', Presentazione di Armando Rigobello, Editori Riuniti University Press, Roma 2012.\n\n==External links==\n{{Commons}}\n{{Wikiquote}}\n{{Wikisource author}}\n* {{Gutenberg author |id=Fichte,+Johann+Gottlieb | name=Johann Gottlieb Fichte}}\n* {{Internet Archive author |sname=Johann Gottlieb Fichte}}\n* {{Librivox author |id=10347}}\n* [http://www.marxists.org/reference/subject/philosophy/works/ge/fichte.htm Outlines of the Doctrine of Knowledge]\n* {{cite SEP |url-id=johann-fichte |title=Johann Gottlieb Fichte}}\n* [http://digilib.bu.edu/nnafs/ The North American Fichte Society]: [http://digilib.bu.edu/nafs/translations.html \"Fichte's Works in English Translation\"]\n* [http://www.zeno.org/Philosophie/M/Fichte,+Johann+Gottlieb Works by Fichte, original German texts]\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20151130092414/http://www.fichte-gesellschaft.de/ Internationale Johann-Gottlieb-Fichte-Gesellschaft]\n* [http://www.kulturwerk-fichte.de/ KULTUR & KONGRESSWERK-fichte] \u2013 Event-location in Magdeburg, named after Johann-Gottlieb Fichte\n* [https://web.archive.org/web/20090511042035/http://www.earlham.edu/~peters/writing/fichte.htm A Case Study in ''Ad Hominem'' Arguments: Fichte's ''Science of Knowledge'']\n\n{{continental philosophy}}\n{{Social and political philosophy}}\n{{Authority control}}\n\n{{DEFAULTSORT:Fichte, Johann Gottlieb}}\n[[Category:1762 births]]\n[[Category:1814 deaths]]\n[[Category:People from Bautzen (district)]]\n[[Category:People from the Electorate of Saxony]]\n[[Category:German Lutherans]]\n[[Category:German nationalists]]\n[[Category:18th-century German writers]]\n[[Category:18th-century philosophers]]\n[[Category:19th-century German writers]]\n[[Category:19th-century German philosophers]]\n[[Category:Christian philosophers]]\n[[Category:Continental philosophers]]\n[[Category:German idealism]]\n[[Category:Idealists]]\n[[Category:German Freemasons]]\n[[Category:German male writers]]\n[[Category:Spinoza scholars]]\n[[Category:Writers from Saxony]]\n[[Category:University of Erlangen-Nuremberg faculty]]\n[[Category:University of Jena faculty]]\n[[Category:Humboldt University of Berlin faculty]]\n[[Category:Deaths from typhus]]\n[[Category:Infectious disease deaths in Germany]]\n", "name_user": "Finnusertop", "label": "safe", "comment": "ce", "url_page": "//en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Johann_Gottlieb_Fichte"}
